000Z","msg":"我覺得cctvb嗰種字幕最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf751d37ba42d1f2c8fb116f466a2828d95ea99","tid":1086503,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba573fff9e294852fbf7da2ff2eeba9c7415dc6","tid":1086503,"uid":113210,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會因為標<span style=\"color: red;\">階</span>體比較適合唔同年齡既人睇<br />\n老一輩睇電腦字體辛苦啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n標楷體<br />\n係電腦字體嘅一種<br />\n如果長時間睇字、長文、字幕，標楷體唔會係睇得舒服嘅字體<br />\n同埋個人覺得標楷體好老土，唔靚<br />\n<br />\n電影公司真係食撚左屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:18:33.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"8e0c17296cca9e25b40d824dbc8480e180c8ef06","tid":1086503,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"其實用黑體係易睇啲嘅"},{"pid":"2343bff0349b17f58036a66d75136eb7c7b4e0df","tid":1086503,"uid":113210,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"edf751d37ba42d1f2c8fb116f466a2828d95ea99","tid":1086503,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba573fff9e294852fbf7da2ff2eeba9c7415dc6","tid":1086503,"uid":113210,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會因為標<span style=\"color: red;\">階</span>體比較適合唔同年齡既人睇<br />\n老一輩睇電腦字體辛苦啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n標楷體<br />\n係電腦字體嘅一種<br />\n如果長時間睇字、長文、字幕，標楷體唔會係睇得舒服嘅字體<br />\n同埋個人覺得標楷體好老土，唔靚<br />\n<br />\n電影公司真係食撚左屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:18:33.000Z","msg":"Source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>咩係標楷體？</strong><br />\n唔知你有冇印象，細個寫楷書字帖，<br />\n標楷體就係原自楷書，<br />\n書法講求美感，寫字時，尾部會拉多啲出嚟等... （唔知點形容，希望你明）<br />\n標楷體仍保留咗少少少少楷書嘅特點，<br />\n字體並非四正<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/HvGn5zt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FHvGn5zt&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=0cf6f84e\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/HvGn5zt</a><br />\n<br />\n文章排版上，當所有標楷體密密麻麻排埋一齊就會有種唔夠整齊，大小不一嘅感覺<br />\n(參考說法：<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1518253026.A.4BE.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmovie%2FM.1518253026.A.4BE.html&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=aff902c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1518253026.A.4BE.html</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>何謂適合嘅字幕字體？</strong><br />\n可於最短時間內閱讀及理解<br />\n<br />\n姐係功能性高，易讀性高嘅字體比較合適做字幕，<br />\n一般會叫呢類字體做中性字體，姐係冇個性嘅字體，以減低觀者對字體嘅注意力，專注接收訊息<br />\n例如：黑體、明體<br />\n<br />\n而標楷體就係「有個性」嘅字體，<br />\n本身就有陣文化色彩，仿古味道，<br />\n放入現代排版，無論點用都覺得老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但中文教科書除外， <br />\n我贊成小學中文課文繼續用標楷體，<br />\n因為本身就係手寫字，最接近我地書寫習慣，我地會以佢為標準學寫字、筆畫<br />\n最近見到啲小朋友學寫字 跟晒明體、黑體，<br />\n寫到奇奇怪怪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n令人討厭的標楷體的一生：<a href=\"https://blog.justfont.com/2014/11/biaukai-a-life/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.justfont.com%2F2014%2F11%2Fbiaukai-a-life%2F&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=ffa7b7eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.justfont.com/2014/11/biaukai-a-life/</a><br />\n<br />\n以上都係我個人理解，仲學習緊<br />\n有錯請指教"},{"pid":"7400306751a21a761c3d6fc234464078cadf3666","tid":1086503,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ccf7c7c4382433c2bd15eaca2a186d5abcb80f3","tid":1086503,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:44:59.000Z","msg":"有字幕咪算好 係外國睇英文片唔會有字幕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"廢"},{"pid":"27aefb2f0b910f3ed9b2013beeef0fd9b74fa7f1","tid":1086503,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7a83b360e3bbd37b95f117fb5b57e3d3b87b0c","tid":1086503,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"其實真係幾核突<br />\n<br />\n中文教科書就話用佢姐"}]}